query:
UPDATE products SET image = CASE 
  WHEN name = 'Le Poulet' THEN 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310419663030752959/XkFJuXKCVOKIOVAn.jpg'
  WHEN name = 'Le Smoked Meat' THEN 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310419663030752959/sUHfGLKLgurntLkx.jpg'
  WHEN name = 'Le Végétarien' THEN 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310419663030752959/GLXQumOimvoRJEeY.jpg'
  WHEN name = 'Salade César' THEN 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310419663030752959/uGVMQcwPJUfiLwYs.jpg'
  WHEN name = 'Café' THEN 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310419663030752959/qThNujZUXiINjNfp.jpg'
  WHEN name = 'Jus d''Orange' THEN 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310419663030752959/KhxfYSjESGPDRCou.jpg'
  WHEN name = 'Thé Glacé Maison' THEN 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310419663030752959/AghmOnRJGuaLjOrG.jpg'
END
WHERE name IN ('Le Poulet', 'Le Smoked Meat', 'Le Végétarien', 'Salade César', 'Café', 'Jus d''Orange', 'Thé Glacé Maison')
